<p><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">地址：札幌市中央区宫之森1274</span><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><span style="font-size: 3px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(84, 141, 212);"><strong style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(84, 141, 212);">日本札幌景点之</span></strong>SAPPORO啤酒博物馆（SAPPORO Beer Museum）</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">札幌是日本啤酒的发源地，从1903年开始生产，SAPPORO啤酒的历史就等于是日本啤酒业的缩影。啤酒博物馆陈列日本啤酒发展史、酿酒器具、酿造过程，参观结束后还可以免费畅饮最新鲜的啤酒一杯。隔壁的札幌啤酒园（サッポロビール園）是由非常具有历史感的红砖厂房改造而成。</span><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://7xotew.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/article-180-1.jpg" title="日本札幌旅游攻略（景点篇）_图片_1" style="white-space: normal; float: none;" alt="日本札幌旅游攻略（景点篇）_图片_1"></span></p>
